<plot>Based on the Comedy of Wild Bill Bauer, Dying to Play "Live Coverage of the International Russian Roulette Championships." Hosted by professional sports commentator Ronald Stewart and a slightly brain damaged runner up from last years British tournament, Hank "The Hammer" Johnson. Three contestants compete to the death. The trigger happy, "Crazy" Joe Clemenz; Arnie Bauer: last years "Rookie of the Year" and "The Russian," a 25-year veteran to the sport. Don't forget your raincoat, this competition is guaranteed to get messy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?162901</url></doc>
